	</b>
</p>
<p>
	SMRI - VRD operates and manages the Online Vendor Registration and Accreditation, for the purpose of providing efficient and timely access to all business reports related to Vendor and SMRI – VRD that may be viewed securely from the SM Vendor Portal.
</p>

